        "text": "Hard to put into words how phenomenal it is to work with Kalen and her team. They are truly the best to do it. Not only do they guide you through every step of the wedding photo journey, but they do it with an immense amount of care and intention. It’s such a personal decision to pick out a wedding photographer — you spend all day with them! And I couldn’t be more grateful we went with Kalen and her team. Cannot recommend them enough! Oh, and the photos were absolutely SPECTACULAR!! ❤️"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2026-06",
        "text": "Kalen is the most talented photographer in the Denver metro area, full stop. What makes her the best is not just her tactical skills (eye for details, great angles, creative locations and photo framing) but her genuine enthusiasm and care for the clients. She's authentic, loves what she does, and is unbelievably encouraging and good at directions when she wants you to pose. I'm someone who feels awkward being the model but Kalen had me loose and embracing it in no time. Kalen shot my and my wife's engagement shoot, rehearsal dinner, and wedding day. The photos are stunning, surpassing even our own high expectations. Hire her immediately!"
      },
